I must hurry to arrange
my marriage plans today.

28:44.167 --> 28:47.967
He wants to marry my Rosina!

28:48.300 --> 28:50.566
The doddering old fool!

28:51.401 --> 28:54.100
But who is this Don Basilio?

28:54.300 --> 28:59.900
A matchmaker and conniver,
without a penny or a conscience.

